bers.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/minimark.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: From Hobbess to Shobby to Seboa and the serverwide GM sy</span><hr size=1> Actually, I kinda agree with the GM in this situation.  I get tired of all the cute little real-world references people put in their names.  Joke names detract from the roleplaying aspect of the game, IMO.<br><br>Your situation got aggravated when you tried to pull a fast one and just spell Hobbes backwards.  Had you *started* the game with the name Sebboh I doubt you would have ever had any problems, though. <p><br><center><TABLE WIDTH=374 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=10 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><a href="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/fury" target="_blank"><IMG SRC="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/guild-button.jpg" WIDTH=56 HEIGHT=125 ALT="Guild Website" border=0></a></TD><TD ROWSPAN=2><IMG style="border: medium outset #999999" SRC="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/kragblade.jpg" WIDTH=262 HEIGHT=250></TD><TD><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=120506" target="_blank"><IMG SRC="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/magelo-button.jpg" WIDTH=56 HEIGHT=125 ALT="Magelo Profile" border=0></a></TD></TR><TR><TD><a href="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/" target="_blank"><IMG SRC="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/homepage-button.jpg" WIDTH=56 HEIGHT=125 ALT="Personal Homepage" border=0></a></TD><TD><a href="http://www.cafepress.com/tipop" target="_blank"><IMG SRC="http://members.telocity.com/~Tipop2000/store-button.jpg" WIDTH=56 HEIGHT=125 ALT="Bauer & Tipop's EQBeastlord Store" border=0></a></TD></TR></TABLE></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/uschezar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Schezar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Savage Hunter</span><br>  Posts: 516<br> <font color=#871F78>(8/15/02 1:03:31 pm)</font>